These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: begonia, rose, tulip, daisy, amaryllis
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: crime, family, satire, western, zombie
There are 5 different nationalities: british, chinese, egyptian, malaysian, turkish
House: gothic-revival, farmhouse, modern, colonial, victorian
 1. the victorian house is on the right of the modern house##1
 2. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
 3. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 4. the person who growstulip is the person who growstulip##1
 5. the gothic-revival house is the person watching crime movies##1
 6. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
 7. the british is on the left of the egyptian##1
 8. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the colonial house##1
 9. the person who growsdaisy is on the far right##1
10. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the modern house##1
11. the person who growsamaryllis is between the chinese and the person watching zombie movies##2
12. the malaysian is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
13. the turkish is on the right of the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Flower      | begonia        | rose | amaryllis     | tulip   | daisy |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | family      | western | zombie   | crime    |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | chinese     | british | egyptian | turkish  |
| House           | farmhouse | modern      | victorian     | colonial   | gothic-revival     |

