.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: skiing, sailing, tennis, climbing, cycling
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: country, d&b, disco, r&b, techno
There are 5 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, indian, polish, spanish
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: spy, drama, epic, mystery, action
 1. the person watching action movies is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of techno is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the dutch##1
 5. the person watching drama movies is between the chinese and the fan of techno##2
 6. the person watching mystery movies is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 7. the fan of country is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
 8. the indian is the fan of r&b##1
 9. the indian is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
10. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
11. the indian is the person who's sport is tennis##1
12. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Sport         | climbing | skiing | cycling    | sailing  | tennis    |
| Music-Genre   | techno    | d&b       | disco      | country | r&b        |
| Nationality   | spanish   | dutch     | chinese    | polish  | indian     |
| Movie-Genre     | epic    | drama | action | mystery | spy |

