.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: collecting, filmmaking, puzzles, rock-climbing, singing
House: palace, modern, wooden, ranch-style, cottage
There are 5 different favourite colors: blood-red, blue, purple, black, aquamarine
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, rowing, tennis, volleyball
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who likes blue##1
 2. the person who's sport is tennis is in the middle##1
 3. the person who likes black is in the middle##1
 4. the palace house is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
 7. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 8. the palace house is on the right of the modern house##1
 9. the person who likes purple is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is badminton is the ranch-style house##1
11. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
13. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the cottage house and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | collecting | singing     | puzzles   | filmmaking   | rock-climbing |
| House   | cottage  | modern | palace | ranch-style | wooden        |
| Color   | purple      | blue      | black       | aquamarine       | blood-red       |
| Sport         | basketball | volleyball  | tennis    | badminton    | rowing        |

