.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-5::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, juice, lemonade, milk, mirinda
There 5 different types of food: apricot, broccoli, lettuce, orange, watermelon
The people use 5 different means of transport: roller, scooter, quad-bike, car, tram
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, havana, prince, aristoff, swisher
 1. the havana-smoker is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
 2. the person eating orange is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
 3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
 4. the person drinking lemonade is between the havana-smoker and the person eating apricot##2
 5. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
 6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person eating orange##1
 7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 8. the person driving the tram is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
 9. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
11. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
12. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
13. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Beverage   | milk       | mirinda       | almond-milk   | lemonade      | juice    |
| Food       | watermelon | orange        | apricot       | lettuce       | broccoli |
| Transport        | tram     | scooter        | car | roller        | quad-bike  |
| Cigar      | aristoff | prince | dunhill      | swisher | havana  |

