 1. the fan of soul is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
 2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
 3. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
 4. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the french##1
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 6. the person who likes mauve is between the fan of electronic and the person who's sport is baseball##2
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is the turkish##1
 8. the australian is on the far right##1
 9. the fan of reggae is on the right of the french##1
10. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
11. the fan of hip-hop is between the fan of electronic and the person who's sport is baseball##2
12. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the polish##1
13. the fan of electronic is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |     5      |
