 1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
 3. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 4. the person traveling to paris is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the egyptian##2
 5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in the middle##1
 7. the turkish is on the right of the colombian##1
 8. the mexican is on the far right##1
 9. the person traveling to boston is the turkish##1
10. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
11. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the colombian##1
12. the person traveling to marseilles is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
13. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |     4      |      5       |
