 5. the fan of r&b is on the right of the italian##1
 6. the lawyer is on the right of the polish##1
 7. the italian is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 8. the entrepreneur is the fan of dubstep##1
 9. the person drinking juice is on the far left##1
10. the fan of rock is on the left of the french##1
11. the fan of r&b is between the entrepreneur and the person drinking juice##2
12. the project-manager is on the right of the lawyer##1
13. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |    5    |
| Beverage         | juice      | coffee | iced-tea | fanta | sprite |
