5 different pets are kept: bird, frog, goldfish, lizard, turtle
The people use 5 different means of transport: bus, car, jet-ski, roller, subway
 1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 2. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1
 3. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in the middle##1
 6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 7. the person who's hobby is reading is the owner of the turtle##1
 8. the person who's sport is skiing is between the owner of the goldfish and the person driving the car##2
 9. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
10. the person driving the car is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
11. the owner of the frog is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2      |     3      |       4       |     5     |
| Sport    | soccer        | skateboarding     | skiing        | ice-hockey | cycling     |
| Hobby         | reading | drawing | skydiving | rock-climbing        | gardening |
| Pet         | turtle       | goldfish   | lizard     | frog          | bird      |
| Transport   | bus          | jet-ski    | subway     | car           | roller    |

