 2. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
 3. the american is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 4. the egyptian is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the american##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 7. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 8. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the american##1
 9. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
10. the person who growsorchid is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the train is between the person who growsorchid and the person who's hobby is reading##2
12. the argentine is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
13. the japanese is on the left of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
