.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, iced-tea, milk, sprite
The people have 5 different jobs:  bartender, engineer, entrepreneur, fisherman, pilot
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: july, may, november, march, january
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, ritmeester, cain, dannemann, aristoff
 1. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 2. the fisherman is between the person who's birthday is in november and the entrepreneur##2
 3. the person drinking milk is the fisherman##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in july is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking milk is between the pilot and the ritmeester-smoker##2
 7. the dannemann-smoker is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is the cain-smoker##1
 9. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the pilot##1
10. the bartender is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
11. the entrepreneur is the person who's birthday is in may##1
12. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1
13. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | 7up      | cola         | milk      | iced-tea | sprite     |
| Job           | engineer | entrepreneur | fisherman | pilot    | bartender  |
| Birthday   | march  | may    | july | november    | january |
| Cigar   | cain  | ritmeester        | chaman   | dannemann    | aristoff     |

