.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: cooking, hiking, reading, april-climbing, skydiving
There 5 different types of food: corn, tomato, pepper, blueberry, onion
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: june, november, march, september, april
There are 5 different nationalities: american, australian, egyptian, malaysian, thai
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person eating corn##1
 2. the person eating onion is between the malaysian and the person who's birthday is in april##2
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 4. the person eating onion is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in june is between the thai and the person who's birthday is in march##2
 6. the thai is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 7. the person eating pepper is the person who's birthday is in september##1
 8. the person who's hobby is april-climbing is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 9. the american is the person who's birthday is in november##1
10. the person who's hobby is april-climbing is on the right of the egyptian##1
11. the person eating onion is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
12. the person eating tomato is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
