| Hobby         | reading    | skydiving  | hiking  | cooking      | april-climbing |
| Food   | tomato    | onion   | blueberry | pepper | corn   |
| Birthday   | march | june    | april    | september       | november         |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | australian | thai    | egyptian     | american      |

 